data.description: Elegantly Updated Rancher in Prime Pueblo County! EXCEPTIONAL OFFER: Dive right into homeownership with a whopping $12,000 in Seller Concessions! This unmatched incentive is yours to command—offset your closing costs or introduce a brand-new central HVAC system, use it to furnish your new home or expand this hobby farm.  An opportunity this grand doesn't come around often! Step into a magnificently renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style residence located in desirable Pueblo County, on the Mesa. Spread out over a generous 2,400 square feet, every inch of this home resonates with contemporary elegance and comfort. Distinctive Features: Refined Refresh: Relish in the newly painted interiors and the luxury of pristine carpeting, ensuring every step you take feels both sophisticated and cozy. Modern Culinary & Bath Spaces: The kitchen boasts updated fixtures and finishes with an oversized island. The bathrooms, having undergone meticulous renovations, promise a daily retreat-like experience. Space Aplenty: Unleash your imagination in the partially finished basement. Dreaming of a man-cave, home theater, or an additional suite? The canvas awaits your vision. Hobby Farm Ready: The unique "chicken ready" feature allows for you to start your very own hobby farm and raised garden bed offers a delightful homesteading experience. Life on the Mesa: Reside moments away from downtown Pueblo, the Pueblo Airport, some Colorado's best farm stands
